data.description: Fabulous home for a full time residence or a great weekend getaway! The absolute best views of the lake! Watch the sunrise or reflect off of the lake for the sunsets. The first floor provides an open floor plan with large dining area opening to a spacious living space. Plenty of windows to take in the incredible views with doors leading to the deck. Included in this level is a bedroom and a full bath. Functional kitchen with dining area. Open stairway takes you to the lower level which has two additional bedrooms, bath and family room. The family room is great for all seasons from its brick fireplace to doors leading to gorgeous yard. The yard gently rolls down to the large deck providing plenty of space for lounging and enjoying the beautiful views. Come find the incredible lake lifestyle here for your enjoyment.
